This is a CodeIgniter template using Twitter Bootstrap.

Current versions:
CodeIgniter 2.1.0
Bootstrap 2.0.1
JQuery 1.7.1 (Google CDN linked)

Bootstrap files are located in include/bootstrap

Default route is the application/controllers/template.php controller

template.php controller loads application/views/content_template.php

content_template.php loads application/views/layout/header.php and application/views/layout/footer.php
